					"value": "When players, as the Dark Urge, accept a duel with Orin. And the companions honour the deal of not getting involved in the battle. And the DU was defeated by Orin.\r\n\r\nThis dialog will start. Upon which Orin will want to sacrifice the remaining players with the rest of the temple."
